Package: politeness
Type: Package
Title: Detecting Politeness Features in Text
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Mike Yeomans, Alejandro Kantor, Dustin Tingley
Maintainer: Mike Yeomans <yeomans@fas.harvard.edu>
Description: Detects linguistic markers of politeness in natural language.
    Allows users researchers to visualize and quantify politeness differences
    between groups of documents.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
